'''John Bevier Ackerman''' (April 29, 1909 – June 13, 1981) was the second [[Deputy Director of the National Security Agency|Vice Director]] of the [[National Security Agency]] of the United States and a [[Major General (United States)|Major General]] of the [[United States Air Force]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nsa.gov/about/leadership/former_deputydirectors.shtml|title=Vice Directors of The National Security Agency|publisher=[[National Security Agency]]|accessdate=December 21, 2008}}</ref><ref name="USAF Biography">{{cite web|url=http://www.af.mil/AboutUs/Biographies/Display/tabid/225/Article/107879/major-general-john-b-ackerman.aspx |title=MAJOR GENERAL JOHN B. ACKERMAN|publisher=United States Air Force|accessdate=June 25, 2014}}</ref>

